'''2020年世界单程距离速度滑冰锦标赛'''是第20届[[世界速度滑冰锦标赛|世界单程距离速度滑冰锦标赛]]，于2020年2月13日至16日在美国盐湖城犹他奥林匹克速度滑冰馆进行。这是盐湖城第三次举办单程距离速度滑冰世锦赛。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.teamusa.org/US-Speedskating/News/Featured-News/2017/June/09/US-Speedskating-Awarded-2020-World-Single-Distance-Championships|title=US Speedskating Awarded 2020 World Single Distance Championships|work=[[美国奥林匹克委员会|Team USA]]|date=2017-06-09|access-date=2017-06-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215144449/https://www.teamusa.org/US-Speedskating/News/Featured-News/2017/June/09/US-Speedskating-Awarded-2020-World-Single-Distance-Championships|archivedate=2019-12-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/olympics/story/_/id/19589382/utah-host-speedskating-championships-2020|title=Utah to host speedskating championships in 2020|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=2017-06-09|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628070919/http://www.espn.com/olympics/story/_/id/19589382/utah-host-speedskating-championships-2020|archivedate=2017-06-28}}</ref>

